title: Edy Fire - Freestyle Cypher Instrumental Hip Hop Mix
description:
After searching for years for a good mix of hip hop instrumentals for freestyling over, I decided to compile over 50 tracks that i have collected over the years and throw this together.

Close to 2 hours of seemlessly mixed hip hop instros - old and new - at a constant 92bpm.

Ideal for any freestyle session or cypher or if you just dig listening to instrumental hip hop.

SHOUT OUTS TO: Big Kayo - Dan Tronix - Battlkat - Martial Mart - SFT - Evil Dave
